marker.ph: We are a community of DevOps engineers who has the goal of helping organisations deliver business value faster, through technology, while having fun

I am an experienced leader in delivering Quality Software @ Speed. My main areas of expertise cover DevOps, Agile and Lean transformations, testing automation, technology leadership and continuous deployment. Professional Scrum Master Level I, a certified AWS Solution Architect, committed to deliver business value through technical excellence. I am comfortable in all aspects of IT methodology leadership, from Agile to Lean, to more pre-emptive methodologies such as UP and Waterfall. I have got a long proven track of turning difficult projects into success stories and in re-gaining business trust in difficult situations.
